::'''Clara:''' I know. Miss Topaz already told me! And, she gave me the Source Code!
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} The Source Code?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501030253-->
::'''Clara:''' I don't quite know why yet... I just know that it can be used to control all of the small robots in Belobog. It's really powerful!
::'''Clara:''' Mr. Svarog said that it is super powerful. He said that it will put a very heavy burden on whoever holds it.
::'''Clara:''' I think that Miss Topaz must have chosen to give me the Source Code for a reason... This represents her faith in me. If that is really true, I must work hard to bear this responsibility.
::'''Clara:''' If I can, I hope that I never have to use this power... I don't want to force anyone to do anything. I just hope I can use it to protect everyone I care about.
::'''Clara:''' I will protect the Source Code. I won't let it get into the wrong hands!
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
